_paragraph\" >Use your camera to reveal new objects into the world, use night-vision to see in the darkness and to create new light sources. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your power usage by finding energy sources to recharge your battery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575120/extras/fad8ab18bc7682af03d8d873248ee5f7.poster.avif?t=1760782494\" width=500 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575120/extras/fad8ab18bc7682af03d8d873248ee5f7.webm?t=1760782494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575120/extras/fad8ab18bc7682af03d8d873248ee5f7.mp4?t=1760782494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look and listen carefully around your environment to find the next well and to descend down them even deeper into new and horrifying environments</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 100% Original soundtrack to create an eerie and creepy atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Beautiful graphics powered by Unreal Engine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A fun minigame to play </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Gameplay that increases tension and fear</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Varied environments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Multiple types of enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Takes around an hour to complete</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow me at @namogames everywhere!</p>",
